{"tid":1290290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強烈譴責]連登仔只識圍爐取暖","createTime":"2019-07-06T12:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T12:34:02.000Z","uid":231905,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"851afdc44544d25ccb37666d85a1d154ff7a8330","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"標題黨sor9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登不嬲好多post都好有point。<br />\n其實上得連登嘅9成9都唔係宣傳對象，但係最近對於連登外宣傳似乎越黎越唔夠力<br />\n今次屯公真係一個非常好嘅材料，有巴打提出聯藍抗共等等概念都非常搞得過。<br />\n要做多啲圖，長輩又好，理性分析都好，大力宣揚出去。<br />\n在此想鼓勵下文宣巴打，我地一齊繼續努力，推撚到港共仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日7/7都要叫多啲出面嘅和理非參與呀!"},{"pid":"7e18724abc86ea04801c9fde880b208b4c28d9dc","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:30:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c8825d9413587023f40184492adbe180b220939a","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:30:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"95c49e060b2ed5b7d6e0b9845c502bc24852e305","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"6fc3c2e3a822b21fa22c81abc82ffa7d1ce3bf35","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:30:54.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7104ff54d60869fb89a4c96f9d63952b5aa19ef3","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"70ee4316415610bbbc470f809026eed67c3e0306","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:31:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"f3a5a14c1626177be3c37a0422bf53a687de5483","tid":1290290,"uid":231905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply